---
<section id="equipo" class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32" data-aos="fade-up">
  <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 text-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="200">Nuestro Equipo</h2>
        <p class="max-w-[900px] text-gray-500 md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="300">
          Conozca a las mentes creativas detrás de Smart Suite
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 mt-12">
      <!-- Miembro 1 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="400">
        <div class="relative mb-4">
          <div class="h-40 w-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-emerald-100">
            <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=160&width=160" width={160} height={160} alt="CEO y Fundador" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 bg-emerald-600 text-white p-2 rounded-full">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Alejandro Torres</h3>
        <p class="text-emerald-600 font-medium">CEO y Fundador</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">
          Con más de 15 años de experiencia en la industria hotelera, Alejandro identificó la necesidad de una
          solución integral para la gestión hotelera.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Miembro 2 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="500">
        <div class="relative mb-4">
          <div class="h-40 w-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-emerald-100">
            <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=160&width=160" width={160} height={160} alt="CTO" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 bg-emerald-600 text-white p-2 rounded-full">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4"><rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Sofía Ramírez</h3>
        <p class="text-emerald-600 font-medium">CTO</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">
          Ingeniera de software con especialización en desarrollo móvil y web, Sofía lidera el desarrollo
          tecnológico de Smart Suite.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Miembro 3 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="600">
        <div class="relative mb-4">
          <div class="h-40 w-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-emerald-100">
            <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=160&width=160" width={160} height={160} alt="Director de Producto" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 bg-emerald-600 text-white p-2 rounded-full">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path><polyline points="3.29 7 12 12 20.71 7"></polyline><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="22" y2="12"></line></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Carlos Mendoza</h3>
        <p class="text-emerald-600 font-medium">Director de Producto</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">
          Con experiencia en diseño UX/UI y gestión de productos, Carlos asegura que Smart Suite sea intuitivo y
          satisfaga las necesidades reales de los usuarios.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Contenedor separado para los dos últimos miembros, centrado -->
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-8">
      <!-- Miembro 4 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="700">
        <div class="relative mb-4">
          <div class="h-40 w-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-emerald-100">
            <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=160&width=160" width={160} height={160} alt="Directora de Marketing" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 bg-emerald-600 text-white p-2 rounded-full">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4"><path d="M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2"></path><path d="M19 3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2"></path><path d="M21 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2"></path><path d="M5 21a2 2 0 0 1-2-2"></path><path d="M9 3h1"></path><path d="M9 21h1"></path><path d="M14 3h1"></path><path d="M14 21h1"></path><path d="M3 9v1"></path><path d="M21 9v1"></path><path d="M3 14v1"></path><path d="M21 14v1"></path></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Laura Vega</h3>
        <p class="text-emerald-600 font-medium">Directora de Marketing</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">
          Especialista en marketing digital y estrategia de marca, Laura se encarga de dar a conocer Smart Suite
          en el mercado hotelero.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Miembro 5 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="800">
        <div class="relative mb-4">
          <div class="h-40 w-40 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-emerald-100">
            <img src="/placeholder.svg?height=160&width=160" width={160} height={160} alt="Director Financiero" class="object-cover w-full h-full" />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 bg-emerald-600 text-white p-2 rounded-full">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4"><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"></line><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Miguel Ángel Rojas</h3>
        <p class="text-emerald-600 font-medium">Director Financiero</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2">
          Con amplia experiencia en finanzas y startups, Miguel Ángel gestiona los recursos financieros para
          asegurar el crecimiento sostenible de Smart Suite.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
